{"title":"天平系统3","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2867","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">一个天平，砝码分别为1g、3g、9g、27g、…6561g，每个砝码只有一个，要称重的物品放在天平的左侧，而砝码只允许放在天平的右侧。这样，肯定有一些物品是无法称重的，例如重量为5g的物品就是无法称出来的。现在将由这个系统可以称出来的重量按从小到大的顺序进行排列，得到下列序列：1,3,4,9,10,12,13,27,28,</span><span style=\"\"> </span><span style=\"\">30,31,36,37,39,40,</span><span style=\"\">...</span><span style=\"\">。问其中的第K个重量是多少？</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">输入一个整数K</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes';\">输出对应的第K个重量</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">15</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">40</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">（1</span><span st